703091f-a.text:
Banker Street, north from Meserole Avenue.  On the right is the Rubin paper box factory, and in the left background are tenements on the west side of Franklin Street extending north from Calyer to Oak Streets.  View 2 shows a closer view of the Franklin Street tenements and W.P.A. men working on a highway project at Calyer Street.

June 27, 1935
Views 1,2

Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
